              "value": "<p>The following software releases have been updated to resolve this specific issue:</p><p>Junos OS: 21.2R3-S3, 21.3R3-S5, 21.4R3-S3, 22.1R3, 22.2R3, 22.3R1 and all subsequent releases.</p><p>Junos OS Evolved: 21.3R3-S5-EVO, 21.4R3-EVO, 22.1R3-EVO, 22.2R3-EVO, 22.3R1-EVO, and all subsequent releases.</p>"
